channel.title: When I use a server with silabs client, I can't move
channel.description:
[center]I think this is a java related problem but I've downloaded JDK 6 already and I've added user variables for it..
Anyway, I download this server and I login on it with silab's client but I can't move or anything, and some of the things haven't even loaded completely and I just get disconnected. If I'm doing something wrong or if there is already an answer to this, please point me into the right direction. For example, I'm using funscap3 server on silabs but I can't move or anything, when I do compiler.bat, it says I don't have JDK 5.0 or 6.0 but I do and when I do runserver.bat it loads up.. Also, when I do a pickup command for a newer item like a white h'ween mask but things get slower and it's in the wrong item slot. Btw, I use no-ip.
Any sort of help is appreciated.
[/center]
